                    ifelse(exam_score$full_score >= 80 &  
                            exam_score$full_score <= 89, "B",
                    ifelse(exam_score$full_score >= 70 &  exam_score$full_score <= 79, "C",
                            ifelse(exam_score$full_score >= 60 &  exam_score$full_score <= 69, "D", "E"
                                ))))
